{
  "name": "RPlog_35_ISY_Competition_Banger_vs_Slush",
  "title": "Banger vs. Slush",
  "summary": "In the 35 ISY fighter-simulator championship, Flight Officer Liza Molokai, call sign Slush, faces Marshal Krieg Inrokana (Banger), with the stormtrooper Lazrus among the spectators cheering the underdog. Molokai surprises the Marshal early, getting the drop on him and even scoring a hit that delights Lazrus' table, but Krieg quickly recovers and turns the tables with veteran flying. Slush refuses to lay down, pressing reckless, unpredictable attacks that keep the duel dangerous despite her depleting shields. Krieg, wary of her teeth much as he was with Vapor, works methodically to break her down. In the end the Marshal's skill prevails, though Slush earns respect for landing blows on him.",
